#. [objectives]
#. EASY difficulty; avoid any unnecessary vagueness in this hint (some vagueness will be inevitable here though):
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:389
msgid ""
"When facing an unknown situation, take into account details from story and "
"dialog to inform your strategy."
msgstr ""
"未知の状況に直面した際は、作戦を立てるためにストーリーとダイアログを考慮に入"
"れましょう。"

#. [objectives]
#. EASY difficulty, 2nd hint; avoid all vagueness in this hint:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:399
msgid ""
"The dark sorcerer is a strong unit; attack him with multiple units at once "
"and try to force him off his keep."
msgstr ""
"黒魔術師は強力なユニットです。複数のユニットで一度に攻撃するように心がけ、で"
"きれば彼を主塔から離れるように仕向けましょう。"

#. [objectives]
#. EASY difficulty; avoid any unnecessary vagueness in this hint (some vagueness will be inevitable here though):
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:410
msgid ""
"Markings or decorations on hexes may indicate something to be found. If you "
"can, it is usually a good idea to investigate."
msgstr ""
"ヘクス上の印や装飾は、何かが見つかることを示していることがあります。もし可能"
"ならば、調査するというのが一般に良い案です。"

#. [objectives]
#. NORMAL difficulty, 1st hint; hint should be somewhat vague:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:425
msgid "Hm, I wonder where Baran could be?"
msgstr "うーむ、Baran はどこにいるのだろう？"

#. [objectives]
#. NORMAL difficulty, 2nd hint; hint should be somewhat vague:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:435
msgid "Beware: the dark sorcerer is a strong unit."
msgstr "要注意：黒魔術師は強力なユニットです。"

#. [objectives]
#. NORMAL difficulty, 3rd hint; hint should be somewhat vague:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:446
msgid "Try investigating hexes with markings or decorations."
msgstr "印や装飾のあるヘクスを探索してみましょう。"

#. [objectives]
#. It is intentional for this hint to just be question marks; since we are on HARD it is supposed to be confusing:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:461
msgid "???"
msgstr "？？？"

#. [objectives]
#. HARD difficulty, 2nd hint; hint should be even vaguer than the 2nd NORMAL hint for this scenario:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:471
msgid "The dark sorcerer is strong."
msgstr "黒魔術師は強力です。"

#. [objectives]
#. HARD difficulty, 3rd hint; hint should be even vaguer than the 3rd NORMAL hint for this scenario:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:482
msgid "Investigate."
msgstr "探索しましょう。"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:519
msgid ""
"Arvith and his men halt outside of the castle, gazing for a moment at the "
"hulking mass of stone looming in the fog. There is movement in the mist."
msgstr ""
"Arvith と彼の兵士は城の外で停止した。そこで濃霧の中に見え隠れする膨大な量の石"
"材をしばらく凝視した。そこには霧の中での行動があった。"

#. [message]: speaker=Guard_leader
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:524
msgid "Halt! Friend or foe? Give the password."
msgstr "立ち止まれ！仲間か敵か？ 合言葉を言え。"

#. [message]: speaker=Arvith
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:529
msgid "The password is"
msgstr "合言葉は"

#. [option]
#. spoken by Arvith:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:533
msgid "Sithrak!"
msgstr "Sithrak!"

#. [option]
#. spoken by Arvith:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:537
msgid "Eleben!"
msgstr "Eleben!"

#. [option]
#. spoken by Arvith:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:541
msgid "Jarlom!"
msgstr "Jarlom!"

#. [option]
#. spoken by Arvith:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:545
msgid "Hamik!"
msgstr "Hamik!"

#. [message]: speaker=Guard_leader
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:560
msgid "Pass, friend."
msgstr "仲間よ、通りたまえ。"

#. [message]: speaker=Arvith
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:576
msgid ""
"The adept didn’t lead us astray after all. I’ll keep my word, distasteful as "
"it may be; cut him loose, and let’s be rid of him."
msgstr ""
"あの魔術師の言ったことは出たら目ではなかったようだな。約束を守るとしよう。気"
"乗りはしないがな。縄を解いて、奴を放してやれ。"

#. [message]: speaker=Muff Toras
#. EASY difficulty; here Muff Toras is much more polite and servile than he would be on other difficulties:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:598
msgid ""
"Thank you so much for sparing me, Sir Arvith! If I may, please permit to "
"join your forces so that I may redeem myself for having kidnapped your "
"brother!"
msgstr ""
"助けていただき感謝します、Arvith 卿！ できることなら、私をあなたの軍隊に加え"
"てください。そうすれば、あなたの兄弟を誘拐した自分自身の汚名を返上できるかも"
"しれません！"

#. [message]: speaker=Arvith
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:603
msgid "Fine, if you insist."
msgstr "いいとも、やりたいというのなら。"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:609
msgid ""
"Muff Toras will now fight on your side! He is a <i>Dark Adept</i>, which you "
"should already know about from having faced previously!"
msgstr ""
"Muff Toras があなたの味方となりました。彼は<i> 暗黒僧</i>ですが、以前対戦した"
"ことがあるので、特性はもうご存じですよね！"

#. [message]: speaker=Muff Toras
#. NORMAL difficulty; here Muff Toras is going more for flattery than for sincere thankfulness:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:633
msgid ""
"Thank you for your mercy, Sir Arvith! Surely a merciful man such as yourself "
"will permit me to join your forces?"
msgstr ""
"あなたの慈悲に感謝します、Arvith 卿！ あなたのような慈悲深いお方が、私の参軍"
"を認めていただけるのですね？"

#. [message]: role=objector
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:661
msgid ""
"Don't let him! I'll never allow myself to fight alongside a dark magic user "
"like him!"
msgstr ""
"そうはさせない！彼のような黒魔術使いと一緒に戦うなんて、絶対にできない！"

#. [message]: speaker=Arvith
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:666
msgid "Hm..."
msgstr "うーむ..."

#. [option]
#. spoken by Arvith:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:669
msgid "Very well, Muff Toras! You may join my forces!"
msgstr "いいだろう、Muff Toras ！軍に加わってよろしい！"

#. [message]: speaker=Muff Toras
#. [message]: role=objector
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:673
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:706
msgid "Thank you for making the right choice!"
msgstr "有難うございます、その選択に感謝します！"

#. [message]: role=objector
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:678
msgid ""
"Hmph, that's it! I quit! I'm sorry, Arvith, but my moral beliefs against "
"dark magic compel me to leave!"
msgstr ""
"はっ、なんてことだ！オレはやめる！すまんが Arvith 、オレの道徳観は黒魔術と相"
"容れないんだ、オレは降りる！"

#. [option]
#. spoken by Arvith:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:688
msgid ""
"I'm sorry, Muff Toras, but I must take into account my men's objections."
msgstr "すまないな Muff Toras 、部下の反対も考えてやらねばならぬ。"

#. [message]: speaker=Arvith
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:692
msgid ""
"While I cannot permit you to fight alongside us, I shall still permit you to "
"leave unharmed, however."
msgstr ""
"し我々と共に戦うことは許せそうにないが、無傷のままお前がここを去ることは許す"
"がな。"

#. [message]: speaker=Muff Toras
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:697
msgid "Hmph, suit yourself..."
msgstr "ふん、どうぞお好きなように..."

#. [message]: speaker=Muff Toras
#. imagine this is Metal Gear Solid and Solid Snake has just been caught in a spotlight:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:754
msgid "<span color='red' size='large' font_weight='ultrabold'>!</span>"
msgstr "<span color='red' size='large' font_weight='ultrabold'>！</span>"

#. [message]: speaker=Arvith
#. HARD difficulty, so Muff Toras has had different behavior than on the previous two difficulties:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:764
msgid ""
"You! But you gave us the correct passwords though! Why would you lead us "
"true if you were only planning on betraying us?!"
msgstr ""
"おまえ！ 正しい合言葉を我々に教えておきながら！　なぜ、裏切るつもりなのに、"
"我々を導いたのだ？！"

#. [message]: speaker=Muff Toras
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:769
msgid ""
"Hahaha, I tricked you! My plan all along was to lead you into a trap! Hey "
"guards, time to return to duty!"
msgstr ""
"はーっはっは、騙されやがって！お前たちを罠に導くのがオレの計画だ！ おい衛兵ど"
"も、仕事に戻る時間だ！"

#. [message]: speaker=Arvith
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:875
msgid "Argh, the guards have returned! Watch your backs, men!"
msgstr "なるほど、衛兵たちが戻ってきたか！背後に気をつけろ！"

#. [message]: speaker=Arvith
#. directed at Muff Toras:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:890
msgid "Time to correct my mistake of having left you alive!"
msgstr "お前を生かしてしまった私の誤りを正す時だな！"

#. [message]: speaker=Muff Toras
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:902
msgid "Ugh, so much for my trap..."
msgstr "うっ、オレの仕掛けた罠も、これまでだ..."

#. [message]: speaker=Guard_leader
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:912
msgid "Wrong! Die!"
msgstr "違ってるぞ！死ね！"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#. Muff Toras corrects Arvith; possibilities for the variables are the passwords listed previously:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:959
msgid ""
"You fool! I <b><i>told</i></b> you it was $first_pwd_name|! Where did you "
"even come up with $pwd_picked_name from?!"
msgstr ""
"このバカヤロウ！ <b><i> 言っただろう</i></b>、$first_pwd_name だよ！どこから "
"$pwd_picked_name なんてのが出てきたんだ？！"

#. [message]: speaker=Arvith
#. directed at Muff Toras:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:964
msgid "Shut up, kidnapper!"
msgstr "うるさいぞ、誘拐犯！"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:986
msgid "Tutorial: Heavy Infantryman"
msgstr "ユニット情報：重歩兵"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#. "In return" here is to contrast a strength against the weaknesses previously mentioned:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:988
msgid ""
"You have recruited a <i>Heavy Infantryman</i>. Heavy Infantrymen have bulky "
"armor which makes them slow and easy for enemies to hit. In return, they "
"wield a mace for a melee attack which can deal massive <i>impact</i> damage, "
"which is especially powerful against skeletons."
msgstr ""
"<i> 重歩兵</i> を雇用しました。重歩兵は分厚い鎧を着けているので、動きが遅く敵"
"の攻撃を受けやすいユニットです。その代わり、彼らは近接攻撃のためにメイスを振"
"り回し、大きな<i> 打撃</i>ダメージを与えることができ、スケルトンに対して特に"
"強力です。"

#. [message]: speaker=Knago-Brek
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1004
msgid ""
"Haha! We not kill people for long time. Weapon wants blood. We now kill "
"humans!"
msgstr ""
"ハッハッ！ 俺たちは長い間人間を殺していない。武器が血を欲しがっている。今こそ"
"俺たちは人間を殺す！！"

#. [message]: speaker=Arvith
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1009
msgid ""
"My sword-arm shall have a say in who will do the dying. Come on, men, let’s "
"kill some orcs."
msgstr ""
"誰が死ぬことになるかは私の剣を持つ腕が決める。お前達、オークどもを殺すのだ。"

#. [message]: speaker=Arvith
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1021
msgid "One less braggart orc in the world."
msgstr "この世界にはほら吹きオークもいるのだ。"

#. [message]
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1030
msgid "Captain, what are <i>orcs</i> doing this far south?"
msgstr "隊長、こんなに南でオーク達はいったい何をしているのでしょうか？"

#. [message]: speaker=Arvith
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1035
msgid "Good question. Perhaps my brother will have found out."
msgstr "いい質問だ。おそらく我が弟はその答えを発見したのだろう。"

#. [message]: speaker=Guard2_leader
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1152
msgid "Are you our relief arriving? Does this mean we get to leave here now?"
msgstr ""
"お前達は到着することになっている交代か？ これは俺たちが今ここを去ってもよいと"
"いうことか？"

#. [message]: speaker=Arvith
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1157
msgid "Um, yes. Fine. You can go."
msgstr "うむ、そうだ。よいだろう。行ってよいぞ。"

#. [message]: speaker=Guard2_leader
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1162
msgid "Um, you’re supposed to give the password."
msgstr "うむ、お前達は合言葉を伝える事になっているな。"

#. [message]: speaker=Muff Toras
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1179
msgid "Don't worry, he knows it, don't you, Arvith?"
msgstr "まあ、心配するな。彼が知ってるよ、なぁ、Arvith？"

#. [message]: speaker=Muff Toras
#. case where player failed first password challenge; "this" time is as in opposed to the previous one:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1192
msgid "You remember what I told you <b><i>this</i></b> time, right, Arvith?"
msgstr "<b><i> 今回</i></b>教えたやつ、覚えてるよな、Arvith ？"

#. [message]: speaker=Muff Toras
#. Unhandled case handler; probably unreached:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1200
msgid "Um, you do remember what I told you, right, Arvith?"
msgstr "うーん、オレが教えたやつ、覚えてるよな、Arvith ？"

#. [message]: speaker=Arvith
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1209
msgid "Oh, of course. I had nearly forgotten."
msgstr "あぁ、もちろんだとも。 もう少しで忘れるところだった。"

#. [option]
#. spoken by Arvith:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1213
msgid "Akranbral!"
msgstr "Akranbral!"

#. [option]
#. spoken by Arvith:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1217
msgid "Drakanal!"
msgstr "Drakanal!"

#. [option]
#. spoken by Arvith:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1221
msgid "Xaskanat!"
msgstr "Xaskanat!"

#. [option]
#. spoken by Arvith:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1225
msgid "Katklagad!"
msgstr "Katklagad!"

#. [message]: speaker=Guard2_leader
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1238
msgid "Thanks! Irritating little formality, isn’t it?"
msgstr "ありがとう！ 少々形式的でいらいらさせたかな？"

#. [message]: speaker=Guard2_leader
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1248
msgid "That’s the wrong password! These aren’t our relief! Get them!"
msgstr "合言葉が間違ってるぞ！ こいつらは交代ではない！ 奴らを捕らえろ！"

#. [message]: speaker=Muff Toras
#. EASY difficulty; Muff Toras corrects Arvith; possibilities for the variables are the passwords listed previously:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1305
msgid ""
"You fool! How could you remember the first password and then forget that I "
"told you that the second one was $second_pwd_name|? Where did you even get "
"$pwd_picked_name from?"
msgstr ""
"このバカヤロウ！最初の合言葉は覚えていて、2つ目の合言葉は $second_pwd_name だ"
"と言ったのを忘れるとは......。どこから $pwd_picked_name なんてのが出てくるん"
"だ？"

#. [message]: speaker=Muff Toras
#. on NORMAL and HARD Muff Toras still yells at you here, but doesn't tell you the correct password:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1311
msgid ""
"You fool! How could you remember the first password and then forget the "
"second one? Where did you even get $pwd_picked_name from?"
msgstr ""
"このバカヤロウ！最初の合言葉は覚えていて、2つ目の合言葉を忘れるなんて。どこか"
"ら $pwd_picked_name なんてのが出てくるんだ？"

#. [message]: speaker=Muff Toras
#. this is the case where the player failed first password challenge, so Muff Toras is correcting Arvith AGAIN;
#. possibilities for the variables are the passwords listed previously:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1326
msgid ""
"You absolute idiot! You forget not only the first password, but also that I "
"told you that the second password was $second_pwd_name|? Where do you even "
"get these wacky ideas for passwords like $pwd_picked_name from? Actually, "
"you know what, I don't even care; I'm out of here."
msgstr ""
"このバカヤロウ！最初の合言葉はおろか、2つ目のパスワードは $second_pwd_name だ"
"と教えたことも忘れたのか？どこから $pwd_picked_name とかいう変てこな合言葉が"
"出てくるんだ？　実はな、どうでもいいのさ、オレはもう帰る。"

#. [message]: speaker=Muff Toras
#. EASY difficulty; Muff Toras corrects Arvith; possibilities for the variables are the passwords listed previously:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1339
msgid ""
"You fool! I <b><i>told</i></b> you it was $second_pwd_name|! Where did you "
"even come up with $pwd_picked_name from?!"
msgstr ""
"このバカヤロウ！ <b><i> 言っただろう</i></b>、$second_pwd_name だよ！どこか"
"ら $pwd_picked_name なんてのが出てきたんだ？！"

#. [message]: speaker=Muff Toras
#. this line probably won't be reached, but in case it is, "it" refers to the second password that Arvith just forgot:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1345
msgid "You fool! I had told you what it was, too!"
msgstr "このバカヤロウ！ それも教えただろう！"

#. [message]: speaker=Arvith
#. the "...well, in any case" part is so this line works regardless of what came before it;
#. if Muff Toras was yelling at him previously, just assume Arvith is purposefully ignoring him:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1362
msgid ""
"...well, in any case, I think I should better support my men at the front to "
"make sure we can free my brother."
msgstr ""
"うーむ、いずれにしても、確実に弟を解放できるようにするには、俺は前方で俺の仲"
"間を支援するのがいいだろう。"

#. [message]: speaker=Muff Toras
#. Muff Toras has just killed Rotharik and is speaking to him:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1381
msgid ""
"I'm sorry, master, but I have realized the error of my ways in following "
"you. No more! It's time for your schemes to end!"
msgstr ""
"申し訳ありません、ご主人様。でも、あなたに従ったことは間違っていたと気づきま"
"した。もう沢山です！あなたの陰謀はここまでですよ！"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. "speaker=unit" is equivalent to "speaker=Rotharik" here (this is his last breath):
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1388
msgid "Your hand or Tairach’s, death is still death... (argh)"
msgstr ""
"貴様の手にかかろうが Tairach だろうが、死には変わりない・・・（アグッ）"

#. [message]: speaker=Arvith
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1398
msgid "‘Tairach’? Who or what is Tairach?"
msgstr "”Tairach” だと？ Tairach とは何だ、それは物か人か？"

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1403
msgid "There’s a key in his robes."
msgstr "彼のローブの中に鍵がある。"

#. [message]: speaker=Arvith
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1413
msgid ""
"That may well be the key to the cell they’re holding Baran in! I will take "
"it."
msgstr "多分それは、奴らが Baran を捕えている独房の鍵だろう！ 俺が鍵を持とう。"

#. [message]: speaker=Arvith
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1441
msgid "It may be important, I best take it."
msgstr "重要な鍵かも知れん。俺が持っておこう。"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1459
msgid "This castle seems as dark as a cave!"
msgstr "この城は洞窟のように暗いぞ！"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#. EASY difficulty; avoid all vagueness in this hint:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1466
msgid ""
"This castle is under a constant, <i>chaotic</i> time of day (equivalent to "
"permanent night), except for illuminated hexes adjacent to lit stone walls "
"(neutral time of day). Place your units carefully, as your troops will be "
"weaker and enemy units stronger."
msgstr ""
"城の中は常に<i> 混沌</i>に有利な時刻となっています（常に夜であることと同義で"
"す）。ただし、明るい石壁の隣接ヘクスは夜明け・夕暮れとして扱われます。ユニッ"
"トの移動場所には注意しましょう。敵が強化され、味方は弱体化するのですから。"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#. NORMAL difficulty; hint should be somewhat vague:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1474
msgid ""
"This castle is under a constant, <i>chaotic</i> time of day, except for "
"illuminated hexes adjacent to lit stone walls. Keep this in mind when "
"placing your units."
msgstr ""
"城の中は常に<i>混沌</i>に有利な時刻となっています。ただし、明るい石壁の隣接ヘ"
"クスは夜明け・夕暮れとして扱われます。ユニットの移動場所には注意しましょう。"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#. HARD difficulty; hint should be even vaguer than on NORMAL:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1482
msgid ""
"The time of day in this castle is mostly constantly <i>chaotic</i> "
"(exceptions apply)."
msgstr "城の中は常に<i>混沌</i>に有利な時刻となっています（例外あり）。"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1502
msgid "Look what I have found in here! I can count $gold_amt pieces of gold."
msgstr "俺がこの中で見つけたものを見てみろ！ $gold_amt ゴールドはあるぞ。"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1542
msgid "I found Baran. He is in this cell."
msgstr "Baran を見つけた。彼はこの独房の中だ。"

#. [message]: speaker=Baran
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1553
msgid "It’s good to see you, Arvith."
msgstr "あなたが再び戻って来てくれて嬉しく思う。"

#. [message]: speaker=Arvith
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1558
msgid "And you too, brother."
msgstr "お前もだよ。弟よ。"

#. [message]: speaker=Baran
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1563
msgid ""
"The accursed dark sorcerer Rotharik has imprisoned me behind this magically "
"enhanced iron gate. It can only be opened with the correct key. You must get "
"it from him to free me."
msgstr ""
"呪われた黒魔術師の Rotharik が、私をこの魔法で強化された鉄の門の背後に閉じ込"
"めたのです。正しい鍵がなければ開けられません。私を解放するためには、奴から鍵"
"を取ってこなければなりません。"

#. [message]: speaker=Baran
#. Baran is reacting to Muff Toras having found him, and is speaking to him:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1575
msgid ""
"You! You were one of my kidnappers! Why have you returned, to torture me, I "
"assume? Well, you won't break me!"
msgstr ""
"お前！お前は私を誘拐した犯人の一人だな！なぜ戻ってきた？拷問するつもりだな？"
"いいさ、お前に屈することなどない！"

#. [message]: speaker=Muff Toras
#. Muff Toras tries to quiet Baran and explain the situation to him:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1580
msgid ""
"Shush! I'm not here to harm you! Your brother Arvith captured me, but he "
"spared my life, so I work for him now! We're going to get you out of here!"
msgstr ""
"静かに！危害を加えたりしません！私はあなたの兄上の Arvith に捕らえましたが、"
"命を助けられたのです。私は今彼のために働いています！あなたをここから助け出し"
"ます！"

#. [message]: speaker=Baran
#. "deliver" as in "deliver on your promise of freeing me":
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1585
msgid ""
"Hm... I can't say I really trust you after you kidnapped me once, but then "
"again, it's not like I have much choice here, so I might as well wait to see "
"if you can deliver..."
msgstr ""
"ふむ...一度誘拐を働いた君を本当に信用するとは言えないが、選択の余地はほぼない"
"から、助け出すという君の約束が本当かどうか待ってもいいかもしれない..."

#. [message]: speaker=Muff Toras
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1589
msgid "That's all I ask."
msgstr "お願いしますよ。"

#. [message]: speaker=Baran
#. https://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/AsYouKnow
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1594
msgid ""
"Well, as one of my kidnappers, you must already know that I can't just "
"fireball my way out of here, due to the magical enhancements your master — "
"er, I mean, FORMER master Rotharik made to this iron gate."
msgstr ""
"なあ、誘拐犯の一味だから知ってるだろうが、お前の主人...つまり、元主人の "
"Rotharik がこの鉄の門にかけた魔法を強化したせいで、ファイアボールを使ってもこ"
"こから出られないのだ。"

#. [message]: speaker=Muff Toras
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1598
msgid ""
"That's correct; it can only be opened with the correct key. We are working "
"on getting it from Rotharik in order to free you."
msgstr ""
"そうなんです。正しい鍵を使わないと開かないんです。あなたを助け出すため、 "
"Rotharik から鍵を奪おうとしているところです。"

#. [message]: speaker=Baran
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1602
msgid "You'd better be!"
msgstr "そうしてくれ！"

#. [message]: speaker=Baran
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1609
msgid ""
"You must be one of Arvith’s men. Please help me get out of this dungeon in "
"which the accursed dark sorcerer Rotharik has imprisoned me! The iron gate "
"is magically enhanced and can only be opened with the correct key. You must "
"get it from Rotharik to free me!"
msgstr ""
"きみは Arvith 配下の者だね。どうか私をこの牢から救い出してほしい。呪われた黒"
"魔術師の Rotharik が、魔法で強化されたこの鉄の門の中に閉じ込めたのだ。正しい"
"鍵でなければ開けられない。Rothariik から鍵を奪って開放してくれないか！"

#. [message]: speaker=Arvith
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1623
msgid ""
"I have already met, and killed, the sorcerer. Is this the key to which you "
"referred?"
msgstr "私はもうその魔術師に遭遇し、倒したぞ。これがお前が言っている鍵か？"

#. [message]: speaker=Baran
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1627
msgid ""
"Yes, it is. Come, unlock this cell door, and let us depart this place, "
"brother!"
msgstr ""
"そう、それです。こっちへ来てこの独房の扉を開けてください。そしてこの地から解"
"放してください、兄さん！"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#. "we" here is the "royal we":
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1658
msgid ""
"You can now control Baran! However, as he will remain imprisoned for the "
"remainder of this scenario, we shall wait until the next one to give you "
"tips on using him."
msgstr ""
"さあ、Baran を操作できるようになりました！でもこのシナリオでは彼は幽閉された"
"ままですので、操作方法については次のシナリオで紹介します。"

#. [message]: speaker=Baran
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1690
msgid "Thank you for saving me. I... was not certain you would come."
msgstr ""
"助けてくれてありがとう。 私は・・・来てくれないのではないかと不安でした。"

#. [message]: speaker=Arvith
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1695
msgid "Have you no faith in your brother, Baran?"
msgstr "Baran よ、お前はこの兄に信頼を置かなかったのか？"

#. [message]: speaker=Baran
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1700
msgid ""
"It’s not that. Perhaps I deserved to rot here. I failed you. I failed you "
"again."
msgstr ""
"そうではありません。ここで朽ち果てるのが当然の報いなのかも知れないと思ったの"
"です。私は兄さんの信頼を裏切りました。一度ならず二度までも。"

#. [message]: speaker=Arvith
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1705
msgid ""
"That is as may be. But you are my brother still. And... I never doubted you "
"would have come for me."
msgstr ""
"そういうことか、でも、依然としてお前は私の弟なのだ。そして・・・私が呼び出せ"
"ば、きっとお前は来ることをもう疑うことはない。"

#. [message]: speaker=Arvith
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1710
msgid ""
"It was no great trial, after all. A few elves, one or two dark sorcerers, a "
"gang of orcs and some undead. Really just a day’s work for the company."
msgstr ""
"おお、何でもなかったぞ。数人のエルフ、1人か2人の黒魔術師、オークの一団と何匹"
"かのアンデッド。実際、我々傭兵にはほんの1日の仕事だ。"

#. [message]: speaker=Baran
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1715
msgid "Thank you for coming to my aid. Let us return to the village."
msgstr "助けに来てくれてありがとう。村へ帰還しましょう。"

#. [unit]: id=Rotharik, type=Orcish Assassin
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1751
msgid "Minion of Tairach"
msgstr "Tairach の手先"

#. [message]: speaker=Rotharik
#. speaker being "Rotharik" here is an id used by both Rotharik himself and the Orcish Assassin ("Minion of Tairach")
#. that replaces him if he's dead; in either case, he is male:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1765
msgid "You are too late! Your brother is already dead! Muahahaha...!"
msgstr "お前は遅すぎた！ お前の弟は既に死んだ！ムッハッハッハッハッ...！"

#. [message]: speaker=Arvith
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:1770
msgid "Argh!!"
msgstr "アー！！！"

#. [scenario]: id=04_Return_to_the_Village
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:5
msgid "Return to the Village"
msgstr "村への帰還"

#. [part]
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:22
msgid ""
"27 V, 363 YW\n"
"Excerpt from the journal of Baran of Maghre\n"
"\n"
"Almost home now. The last week has been full of mixed feelings for me — "
"blissful and difficult by turns. It was wonderful to be out of that dungeon "
"cell and in the sunlight again without the threat of death or worse hanging "
"over my head... but with that behind me, I turned to the almost equally "
"daunting task of making amends with my brother.\n"
"\n"
"Arvith had largely forgiven me by the time he freed me from my cell. All the "
"same, it has taken all of the past week for us to rebuild the sense of "
"comfort in each other we once had. It is fortunate that we have been able to "
"take our time getting back — we gave the Grey Woods a wide berth, and on our "
"way around it we traveled through some truly beautiful countryside. It has "
"given us plenty of time to talk."
msgstr ""
"Wesnoth 暦 363 年 5 月 27 日\n"
"Maghre の Baran の記録より引用\n"
"\n"
"今はここが故郷のようになってしまった。先週、私は実に多くの感情を味わった。そ"
"れは楽観と悲観が交互に訪れるようなものだった。最初の頃はこの地下牢を出て死の"
"恐怖（最悪の場合私の首が吊るされること）もなく、陽射しを目にすることを夢見た"
"が・・・今となってはその感情は私の中を通り過ぎてしまった。私は兄と共にこれと"
"同じぐらいの恐ろしい償いをさせることだけを考えている。\n"
"\n"
"Arvith は私を牢から解放するまでには、おおよそ私のことを許してくれたようだっ"
"た。一方、この一週間のあいだに、我々兄弟にかつてあったお互いを満足させる感覚"
"を再び取り戻すことができた。我々の時間を巻き戻すことができたのは幸いだった。"
"我々は灰色森に大きなベッドを作ってきたし、その途中では本当に美しい田園地帯を"
"旅した。当時は二人で会話する時間が十分すぎるほどあった。"

#. [part]
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:30
msgid ""
"27 V, 363 YW\n"
"Excerpt from the journal of Baran of Maghre\n"
"\n"
"Though I am more at ease now, my thoughts often turn back to Toen Caric. We "
"should have been able to repel the orcs without great loss — the pincer "
"attack Arvith devised would surely have carried the day but for me. It was "
"reckless of me to leave my men behind — I wounded the warlord and forced him "
"to flee the field, but the cost far outweighed the gain. Those under my "
"command could have been saved if I had remained with them.\n"
"\n"
"I can hardly blame Arvith for having taken their deaths ill, and I can never "
"undo the wrong that I have done, but I suppose that time heals some things. "
"We return to the village as brothers once more.\n"
"\n"
"But I am still troubled. I wonder... is this sense of foreboding I feel "
"merely a remnant of my time locked away in that dungeon, or is it a sign of "
"something real?"
msgstr ""
"Wesnoth 暦 363 年 5 月 27 日\n"
"Maghre の Baran の記録より引用\n"
"\n"
"なんとか平静を取り戻せているが、私はしばしば Toen Caric のことを思い出す。"
"我々はオークに対して大きな損害もなく撃退できたはずだった。Arvith の考案したは"
"さみ撃ち攻撃で勝敗は決定的だった、私さえいなければ。私はその時、無謀にも仲間"
"から離れて突進してしまったのだ。私はオークの将軍を負傷させ戦場から退散させた"
"が、その代償は実に大きかった。私が指揮していた仲間達は私が彼らと共にいたなら"
"命を落とさずに済んだだろう。\n"
"\n"
"彼らの死を重く受け止めていた Arvith を責めることなどできないし、私が犯した失"
"敗はもう決して取り消すことができない。しかし、時間がいろいろなことを癒してく"
"れたのではないだろうか？そのように私は思っている。我々はあの村へ再び兄弟とし"
"て戻るのだ。\n"
"\n"
"しかし、依然として私は胸騒ぎがするのだ。これは一体... この地下牢に閉じ込めら"
"れていたときの単なる名残か、それとも、本当に何かの前触れだろうか？"

#. [side]: type=Orcish Warlord, id=Tairach
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:83
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/05_Epilogue.cfg:56
msgid "Tairach"
msgstr "Tairach"

#. [side]: type=Longbowman, id=Reeve Hoban
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:113
msgid "Reeve Hoban"
msgstr "顧問官 Hoban"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:136
msgid "Find out what is happening in the village"
msgstr "村で何が起こっているのかを見つける"

#. [objectives]
#. EASY difficulty; avoid all vagueness in this hint:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:154
msgid ""
"Recruit or Recall some high-move units to be able to see as far as possible "
"through the fog for approaching units."
msgstr ""
"接近するユニットに対応するため、高い移動力のユニットを雇用あるいは召還し、で"
"きるだけ遠く霧を見通せるようにしましょう。"

#. [objectives]
#. NORMAL difficulty; hint should be somewhat vague:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:158
msgid "Watch your visibility with this fog."
msgstr "霧の中では視界の範囲に気をつけてください。"

#. [objectives]
#. HARD difficulty; hint should be even vaguer than on NORMAL:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:162
msgid "Watch out!"
msgstr "気を付けて！"

#. [message]: speaker=Arvith
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:186
msgid ""
"There. The village is just across those hills, and already I see men coming "
"to greet us!"
msgstr ""
"あそこだ。お前の村はこの丘を越えたところだ。そして、すでに俺たちを歓迎する男"
"達が来るのが見えるぞ！"

#. [message]: speaker=Baran
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:205
msgid ""
"No, they are fleeing from something. We must find out what is happening over "
"there!"
msgstr ""
"いや、彼らは何かから逃げている。俺たちはあそこで何が起っているのかはっきりさ"
"せなければなりません！"

#. [message]: speaker=Arvith
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:210
msgid "Men! Ready your arms!"
msgstr "お前達！ 武器を構えろ！"

#. [message]: speaker=Baran
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:215
msgid "We should find Reeve Hoban. Maybe he knows what is going on here."
msgstr ""
"あそこに行って、顧問官の Hoban と話すべきです。 たぶん彼はここで何が起きてい"
"るか知っているでしょう。"

#. [message]: speaker=Arvith
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:221
msgid "Aye, I shall have to assign some of my men to scout for him!"
msgstr "ああ、部下数名を偵察に当たらせるべきだろうな！"

#. [message]: speaker=Baran
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:226
msgid ""
"I would suggest recruiting or recalling some footpads or horsemen for that "
"task!"
msgstr "それには、追いはぎか騎兵を数名、雇用または召喚するほうがよいでしょう！"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:240
msgid "Tutorial: Baran"
msgstr "人物情報：Baran"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:241
msgid ""
"Baran is now free for you to use to his full potential! Baran is a <i>Red "
"Mage</i>. He is unique among your units in that he has a <i>neutral</i> "
"alignment. He has a strong ranged attack in which he hurls powerful magical "
"fireballs at enemies. Unfortunately, the enemies against which these "
"fireballs are strongest (undead and wood-based enemies) aren't available "
"here at the end of this campaign for you to fry. Baran can also do a weak "
"melee attack with his staff, dealing <i>impact</i> damage to enemies."
msgstr ""
"Baran を自在に操作できるようになりました！ Baran は<i> 赤魔術師</i>で、あなた"
"の軍隊の中で唯一、中立属性を持っています。強力な魔法のファイアボールを敵に放"
"つ、遠隔攻撃の持ち主です。残念ながら、このファイアボール攻撃で懲らしめるのが"
"特に有効な敵（アンデッドや巨木系ユニット）は、このキャンペーンの終わりには登"
"場しません。また、Baran は、あまり強力ではない杖による近接攻撃もでき、打撃ダ"
"メージを与えることができます。"

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:257
msgid "We’re almost there!"
msgstr "我々はほぼ到着したぞ！"

#. [message]: speaker=Baran
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:262
msgid "That warlord! It’s..."
msgstr "あれがオークの将軍です！あれは..."

#. [message]: speaker=Arvith
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:267
msgid "Yes, I’d know that face anywhere. Especially after what you did to it."
msgstr ""
"おお、私はどこでも直面している状況を理解している。特にお前が奴に傷を追わせた"
"後ではな。"

#. [message]: speaker=Baran
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:272
msgid "The warlord from Toen Caric."
msgstr "あのオークの将軍は Toen Caric にいた奴です。"

#. [message]: speaker=Tairach
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:277
msgid "You! The mage who scarred me with fire! KILL THEM!"
msgstr "貴様！俺に炎で傷跡を残しやがった魔術師だな！皆殺しだ！"

#. [message]: speaker=Baran
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:282
msgid "Let’s finish what we started, brother."
msgstr "私達が始めたものを終わらせましょう、兄上。"

#. [message]: speaker=Arvith
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:287
msgid "Aye. I’ll be the right arm, and you’ll be the left. Let’s go!"
msgstr "そうだな、私は右腕でお前は左腕となることができる。さあ行こう！"

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:326
msgid "Hey look! It's Reeve Hoban!"
msgstr "おい、あれは顧問官 Hoban だ！"

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:332
msgid "One of Reeve Hoban's men!"
msgstr "顧問官 Hoban の兵の一人だ！"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:337
msgid "Hey Reeve! Look who showed up!"
msgstr "やあ、Reeve！誰が来たかと思ったよ！"

#. [message]: speaker=Reeve Hoban
#. Reeve starts to say "Arvith" but then interrupts himself:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:384
msgid ""
"Hello Arv-wait, what's this? Why do you have a dark mage with you, Arvith?!"
msgstr ""
"いやあ、Ar... 待って、何ですかこれは？ どうして黒魔術使いと一緒にいるんです"
"か、Arvith！"

#. [message]: speaker=Arvith
#. "Hold" as in "Hold up" or "Hold your fire" or "Hold your horses":
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:389
msgid ""
"Hold, fair Reeve. This mage agreed to fight alongside me after I spared his "
"life."
msgstr ""
"待ってくれ、正義漢の Reeve 。この魔術師は、共に戦うと決めたんだ、私がその命を"
"救ったのさ。"

#. [message]: speaker=Reeve Hoban
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:393
msgid ""
"Well, if you trust him, I guess that I can do so, as well. Anyways, I am "
"glad that you have returned."
msgstr ""
"ええ、あなたが信頼してるのなら、私も信じられる。ともかく、戻ってきてくれて何"
"よりです。"

#. [message]: speaker=Reeve Hoban
#. Now that we lift some fog above, Reeve being able to see Arvith is probably literal now, although there's still a chance it's figurative:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:400
msgid "I am glad to see you returned."
msgstr "あなたが再び戻って来てくれて嬉しく思います。"

#. [message]: speaker=Baran
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:407
msgid "No gladder than I am to be here. But what has happened to Maghre?"
msgstr "ここに居られるより嬉しいことは無い。しかし、Maghre に何があったのだ？"

#. [message]: speaker=Reeve Hoban
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:412
msgid ""
"Soon after you departed we were beset by orcs. With half the men of Maghre "
"gone, we could not stop them."
msgstr ""
"あなたが出発したすぐ後、私達はオークに包囲されました。Maghre の男たちの半数が"
"いなくなったので、私達は奴らを止められませんでした。"

#. [message]: speaker=Reeve Hoban
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:417
msgid ""
"The orcish warlord aims to enslave us. We will not be able to hold out for "
"much longer."
msgstr ""
"オークの将軍は私たちを奴隷にするのが目的です。 私達はもうこれ以上長くはもたな"
"いでしょう。"

#. [message]: speaker=Reeve Hoban
#. some archaic wording here; "fell" in the sense of "strong and cruel" or "eager and unsparing":
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:423
msgid ""
"Have a care, his men are fell fighters and have killed many. Very few remain "
"who can bear arms, but I will send them to aid you in battle."
msgstr ""
"注意して下さい。 奴の兵士達は凶暴な戦士で、多くの者を殺しました。 我々には武"
"器を手にできる者はほんのわずかしか残っていませんが、戦闘であなた達を助けるた"
"めに彼等を送りましょう。"

#. [message]: speaker=Reeve Hoban
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:449
msgid ""
"Ungh... My time has come... Arvith... Baran... the defense of Maghre now "
"falls to the two of you..."
msgstr ""
"あぁ... 私の番が来たようです... Arvith 卿... Baran 卿... Maghre の防衛は今、"
"あなた方お二人に委ねられます..."

#. [message]: speaker=Arvith
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:454
msgid "No! Reeve!"
msgstr "だめだ！ Reeve ！"

#. [message]: speaker=Baran
#. "this" = the killing of Reeve Hoban:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:460
msgid "You orcs will pay for this!"
msgstr "お前たちオークにこの償いはしてもらう！"

#. [message]: speaker=Arvith
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:472
msgid ""
"...well, we can't sit around mourning Reeve while we are still beset by "
"orcs... To the defense of Maghre, men!"
msgstr ""
"...この、オークに包囲されている状況では Reeve の死を嘆くのは後回しにするしか"
"ない... Maghre を守るんだ、男たちよ！"

#. [message]: speaker=Baran
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:477
msgid "Maybe we can take up his position for him?"
msgstr "ひょっとすると、我々が彼の代わりを務めることができるのでは？"

#. [message]: speaker=Arvith
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:482
msgid "We shall see!"
msgstr "ああ、そうするとも！"

#. [message]: speaker=Reeve Hoban
#. directed at Arvith:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:503
msgid ""
"Here, have some gold. You could probably put it to better use than I can."
msgstr "この gold をどうぞ。私が持ってるより、ずっと役に立てられるでしょう。"

#. [message]: speaker=Arvith
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:509
msgid "It appears Reeve left behind some gold in his keep!"
msgstr "Reeve が城に残してくれたのは gold だったようだな！"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:560
msgid "Slay the Orcish Warlord to free the village"
msgstr "村を解放するためにオークの将軍を殺害する"

#. [objectives]
#. EASY difficulty; avoid all vagueness in this hint:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:578
msgid "You can use Reeve Hoban’s keep to recruit or recall additional units."
msgstr ""
"顧問官 Hoban の主塔を用いて追加のユニットを雇用あるいは召還することができま"
"す。"

#. [objectives]
#. NORMAL difficulty; hint should be somewhat vague:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:582
msgid "Have Arvith make use of Reeve Hoban’s keep."
msgstr "Arvith に顧問官 Hoban の城の主塔をうまく活用させましょう。"

#. [objectives]
#. HARD difficulty; hint should be even vaguer than on NORMAL:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:586
msgid "Use Reeve Hoban’s keep."
msgstr "顧問官 Hoban の主塔を使おう。"

#. [message]: speaker=Tairach
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:627
msgid "Today, you shall pay for disfiguring my face, mage!"
msgstr "魔術師、今日こそ俺の顔を傷つけたツケを返してもらうぞ！"

#. [message]: speaker=Baran
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:632
msgid ""
"I have already paid with the lives of my men at Toen Caric. It is time I "
"righted that mistake and finished this once and for all."
msgstr ""
"そのために Toen Caric の仲間達の命が犠牲になった。ここでその過ちを正し、全て"
"を終わらせてみせます。"

#. [message]: speaker=Tairach
#. directed at Arvith:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:673
msgid "You again!"
msgstr "またお前かよ！"

#. [message]: speaker=Arvith
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:678
msgid "It is time for me to finish what Baran started!"
msgstr "Baran が始めたことだ、今度は私が方を付ける番だ！"

#. [message]: speaker=Tairach
#. directed at Muff Toras:
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:719
msgid ""
"Hey wait, weren't you one of that insignificant mage Rotharik's men? Weren't "
"you supposed to be capturing Baran and bringing him to me?"
msgstr ""
"おい待てよ、お前、あのつまんねえ魔術師 Rotharik の手下だったヤツじゃねえか？ "
"Baran をとっ捕まえて、オレのとこにしょっ引いてくるんじゃなかったのか？"

#. [message]: speaker=Muff Toras
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:724
msgid ""
"Yes, that was originally the plan. However, I've changed my mind: I'd much "
"rather kill you instead!"
msgstr ""
"ああ、そうだったよ最初はな。だがよ、心変わりしちまったわけよ、アンタを殺そ"
"うってな！"

#. [message]: speaker=Arvith
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:740
msgid ""
"It is finished. We’ve defeated him at last. It was good to have you at my "
"side, Baran."
msgstr ""
"終わった。ついに我々は奴を倒したのだ。 Baran よ、その瞬間にお前が私の隣にいた"
"ことは喜ばしいことであった。"

#. [message]: speaker=Baran
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:745
msgid ""
"So much has been destroyed. It will be difficult to repair all that the orcs "
"and undead have wrecked. And they could come again."
msgstr ""
"とても多くのものが破壊されました。オークとアンデッドが破壊した物を復旧するの"
"には苦労することでしょう。そして、奴らはまた来るかもしれません。"

#. [message]: speaker=Arvith
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:750
msgid ""
"I must go back to earning my living. But we have our amulets, little "
"brother. If you are beset again, I will come."
msgstr ""
"私は生活費を稼ぐために戻らなければならない。しかし、我々にはアミュレットがあ"
"るではないか、弟よ。もしお前がまた困難に陥ることがあれば、私は何としても駆け"
"つけるだろう。"

#. [message]: speaker=Arvith
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:769
msgid "I don’t think we can rescue anyone from these villages. It is too late."
msgstr "この村々から誰も救出できるとは思えない。 遅すぎた。"

#. [message]: speaker=Baran
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/04_Return_to_the_Village.cfg:774
msgid "I was too weak to protect these people. Oh, why did this happen to me?!"
msgstr "私はこの人々を守るには弱すぎた。 ああ、なぜこんなことになったのだ？！"

#. [scenario]: id=05_Epilogue
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/05_Epilogue.cfg:5
msgid "A Tale of Two Brothers — Epilogue"
msgstr "２人の兄弟の物語 ─ エピローグ"

#. [part]
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/05_Epilogue.cfg:18
msgid ""
"22 IX, 365 YW\n"
"Excerpt from the journal of Arvith of Maghre\n"
"\n"
"Maghre is looking much better than the last time I saw it. Baran has done "
"wonders in two years. The village is rebuilt, and the surrounding farmlands "
"are restored and reoccupied. Despite my brother’s worries, our people have "
"faced no new threats in that time.\n"
"\n"
"It has been more difficult to stay away in those two years, but I have my "
"calling and Baran has his, and we have had little opportunity to meet again. "
"But as the company and I are passing through this part of the kingdom with a "
"new patron, I have asked leave of him to visit my brother and he gave it."
msgstr ""
"Wesnoth 暦 363 年 9 月 22 日\n"
"Maghre の Arvith の記録より引用\n"
"\n"
"Maghre は私が前回見た時よりもかなり良くなっているように見える。Baran はこの二"
"年に数々の奇跡を成し遂げた。村は再建され、周辺の農地も修復されるか再び開墾さ"
"れた。我が弟の心配に反して、我々の民衆はその間に新たな脅威に直面することはな"
"かった。\n"
"\n"
"この二年で離れて暮らすことはより困難になったが、私はお互いに連絡するためのお"
"守りを持ち続けたし、弟もそうした。そのため、再会する機会は殆どなかった。しか"
"し、新たな主人と共に王国のこの地方を往来していたので、私は彼の元を離れて弟の"
"所へ帰ることを頼んで、彼から許しを得た。"

#. [part]
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/scenarios/05_Epilogue.cfg:27
msgid ""
"22 IX, 365 YW\n"
"Excerpt from the journal of Arvith of Maghre\n"
"\n"
"This patron is, of all things, an elf. I never thought I’d befriend one, but "
"he is less arrogant than the rest. Kalenz, he calls himself. He’s seen too "
"much; I can tell that just by meeting his eyes. I think we will have to work "
"for our pay soon.\n"
"\n"
"In the meantime, though, it’s good to relax and enjoy the peace."
msgstr ""
"Wesnoth 暦 363 年 9 月 22 日\n"
"Maghre の Arvith の記録より引用\n"
"\n"
"この主人は、実の所、エルフなのだ。私は彼らの味方になるとは夢にも思わなかった"
"が、彼は他のエルフと違って尊大な所が少ないのだ。彼は自分自身を Kalenz と呼"
"ぶ。彼は偉大だと思う。それは彼の目を見るだけでわかる。まもなく我々は稼ぎに戻"
"らなくてはならないだろうと思う。\n"
"\n"
"しかし、それまでの間平和な時間を楽しむとしよう。"

#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/utils/characters.cfg:6
msgid "Arvith"
msgstr "Arvith"

#. [message]: speaker=Arvith
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/utils/characters.cfg:25
msgid "All is lost now that I am dead..."
msgstr "私が死んだ今、全ては失われた..."

#. [message]: speaker=Baran
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/utils/characters.cfg:43
msgid "It is over, I am vanquished."
msgstr "終わりだ、私は敗北した。"

#. [message]: speaker=Muff Toras
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/utils/characters.cfg:62
msgid "Ugh, I guess I should have seen this coming..."
msgstr "うぅ... こうなるかと、うすうす感じてはいたんだ..."

#. [message]: speaker=Arvith
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/utils/characters.cfg:67
msgid "What a shame, just as he was starting to redeem himself, too..."
msgstr ""
"なんとも残念だ、コイツも自分自身を取り戻そうとしていた矢先だったのに..."

#. [unit]: id=Baran, type=Red Mage
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/utils/characters.cfg:154
msgid "Baran"
msgstr "Baran"

#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/utils/macros.cfg:4
msgid "Hint:"
msgstr "ヒント："

